<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10498775>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Synagris huberti de Saussure. a, habitus in dorsal view. b, male head in frontal view. c, female head in frontal view. d, male mandible in lateral view. e, metanotum and propodeum in posterodorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10498775/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10498779>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Synagris huberti de Saussure, female lectotype of S. huberti var. bimaculata Maidl. a, habitus in dorsal view. b, habitus in lateral view. c, S2 in ventral view. d, labels. Credits: Harald Schillhammer and Manuela Vizek, NHMW, 2023." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10498779/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10498799>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Male genitalia: aedeagus in ventral and lateral view, digitus+volsella. a, Synagris huberti de Saussure. b, Synagris rufopicta Tullgren." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10498799/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10498801>
    dc:description "Figure 8. Distributional map of Synagris (Paragris) species. Produced using the online tool SimpleMappr (Shorthouse 2010)." ;
